              In September 2017, we tested new designs of the sign in badge. The current winner is the variation of the badge on the right side of the screen, over a fullbleed background image.
              <br>
              <br>
              I updated style guide to include new templates and guidance for this new design, changing the number of text layouts, the text sizing at desktop and tablet, and the image requirements. Because of the grid and the homepage’s responsiveness, only imagery that acts as a background was initially accepted.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%- include(process.cwd() + '/app/partials/section-sub-header', {headline: 'Style Guide: Next Steps'}) %>
        <div class="row p-row">
